            <title>[SOLR-1135] snapshot is created in the directory where solr was lauched</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1135</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when a request &lt;/p&gt;

